&lt;li&gt;Strong facilitator in technical conflict—you listen, synthesize, decide, and bring the team with you&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Competence across HTTP, TLS, caching strategies, load shedding, capacity planning, observability, and cost optimization&lt;/li&gt;
