&lt;li&gt;Collaborate closely across Design, Product, Creative Technology, and Engineering teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build, own, and maintain documentation of animation specs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to the impact and culture of the motion design discipline&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
