&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A broad portfolio of professional work showcasing animation craft and technical expertise&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5 years of experience in motion design, preferably for digital products&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A strong foundation in After Effects, with interest or experience in Figma, Rive, and AI tooling&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven ability to thrive in small, fast-paced teams and champion your work to teammates and leadership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A highly organized and iterative creative process&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The ability to work in or relocate to Pittsburgh, PA, Detroit, MI, or New York, NY&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;max-width: 100%;&quot; src=&quot;https://careers.duolingo.com/d26c1c52534fdf7f9587.svg&quot; alt=&quot;icon-star-16px&quot; width=&quot;17&quot; data-is360=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; Exceptional candidates will have...&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
